        <updateDate>2016-03-08T21:58:18Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>People Before Party Act of 2016</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Help America Vote Act of 2002 to prohibit a state from providing a voter, in a federal election, with the opportunity to indicate the selection of a political party as a representation of the selection of an individual candidate. (Thus prohibits voting for a party instead of an individual or "straight-party voting.")</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
